A very simple thesaurus app showing the usage of Redis, Spring Redis Data, Groovy, Java, Gradle and PHP.

What do I need to run this app locally on my machine?

-Redis
    http://redis.io/
-Java JDK
    http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html
    http://openjdk.java.net/
-Gradle/Groovy
    http://www.gradle.org/
-Apache/PHP
    http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/ubuntu/installing-php5-and-apache-on-ubuntu/
-PHPRedis
    https://github.com/nicolasff/phpredis
    http://ricochen.wordpress.com/2012/03/25/install-phpredis-on-ubuntu/